0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"What is Sedex Audit?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:55+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"What is Sedex Audit?Wizms provides the best Sedex audit in UAE, Dubai"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"What is Sedex Audit?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sedex is defined as Supplier Ethical Data Exchangeintroduced to drive ethical business practices. Sedex helps to maintain the ethical information in a simple way.Buyers can manage and view the ethical data and information for multiple suppliers in one place whereas Suppliers can share their ethical information or data for multiple buyers at another secure place. As such the chain moves on.Sedex enables member companies in UAE and Dubai to efficiently manage their ethical and responsible practices of their global supply chains, generating transparency through the provision of a data exchange."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sedex focuses on 4 pillars. Members companies commit to improving their supply chain performance accordingly."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Labour Standards,"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Health & Safety,"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Environment and"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Business Integrity."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The tool used by Sedex is named SMETA (Sedex Members Ethical Trade Audit). To get Sedex Certification choose the right ISO certification consultant"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Reducing the number of audits"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Our ISO consultant in Dubai can help the organizations to monitor sustainable performance in the supply chain more effectively, providing more visibility on the results of Sedex audits. By submitting supply chain Sedex audit results to the database, Wizms help ensuring transparency and re-use of existing Sedex audit data. There is no need for a manufacturer for re-audition to qualify them as suppliers, but rather checks their status in the Sedex database."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Benefits of Sedex Audit"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"SMETA is designed to benefit retailers, consumer brands and their suppliers, reducing duplication of effort in ethical trade auditing. Companies who are not members of Sedex are encouraged to use SMETA as well. Sedex is a comprehensive platform that enables effective management of complex global supply chains, leading to real business benefits for your organization."}],"$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La"]}],"$Lb"]}]}],["$Lc"],"$Ld"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Improvement in reputation"}]
3:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms provides best ISO consultancy Services who demonstrate to stakeholders and customers that they are committed to drive improvements in their supply chain."}]
4:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Gain competitive advantage"}]
5:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Many customers view Sedex Certification as an important part of their sourcing practices and companies increasingly view Sedex membership as a condition of supply chain audit."}]
6:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Reduce risk"}]
7:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The reports available on Sedex Audit, and the Sedex Risk Assessment tool, can help assess the issues occurring in their supply chain that helps to improve supplier relationships. Sedex model encourages increased supplier engagement, helps the organization in UAE to drive ethical and responsible improvements within their supply chain."}]
8:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Save time and money"}]
9:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sedex Audit allows more time and resources to be spent on making improvements rather than completing multiple audits and unnecessary paperwork. SMETA is a new code of conduct or standard to which Sedex audits should be conducted. It is compilation of best practice in ethical trade sedex audit technique, intended for experienced ISO auditors to help them to conduct high quality sedex audits that will be accepted by multiple retailers and brands."}]
a:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sedex Certification in UAE is a most preferred Certification Standard by organizations in UAE from all sectors. Wizms provides ISO Certificate in UAE for all major standards such as ISO 9001:2015, ISO 14001:2015, ISO 27001:2015, ISO 17025:2017, ISO 45001:2018 and more. Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE and provides ISO consulting services in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain and Fujairah. Wizms ISO consultant in Dubai offers top-class ISO consultancy services including ISO Consulting, ISO Certification, ISO Training in UAE, Gap analysis, Documentation, Implementation, and ISO certification audits in UAE."}]
